::KitKat::

She checked the scanners. Megatron, Tarantulus, HellBeast, had gone 
to Aracnia's base. She opened her link. "What is going on Megatron? 
Do you need any help?"

She then checked her long range scanners and found where Destructor 
was at. She opened her link to him. "Destructor, give me the reason 
to move, and we shall." She was following her insticts. And they said 
to follow Destructor.

She looked at Quickstrike. " Get ready, we're moving ourselves."
She opened her link to DarkMouse, Drillbit, Dollen and 
GoldenEye. "Hey all, we're moving. Grab your gear and all we might 
need. We're out of here. We got something that might be better and 
stand up to the Allience better."  At this point, she really had no 
idea what she was doing or where they were going, but her faith in 
her team was strong. She smiled, "And Drillbit, I need to talk to 
you, in private, when you get a moment."

She chuckled quietly to herself. She looked again at Quickstrike. She 
put her hand on his shoulder. "It's good to see you again my frined."
